To build :
- install sbt (http://code.google.com/p/simple-build-tool/wiki/Setup)
- clone this repo :
	git clone git@github.com:ochafik/nabab.git
- build with sbt :
	cd nabab && sbt update compile
- run (choose the Baya main class) :
	sbt run